xtables-addons-asn (2.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major release with comprehensive modernization and bug fixes
  * Complete project infrastructure overhaul
  * Enhanced ASN data processing with reliable script execution
  * Comprehensive testing framework with 5 test suites
  * Modern build system supporting both autotools and CMake
  * Professional CI/CD pipeline with multi-platform support
  * Debian/Ubuntu packaging with systemd integration
  * Cross-platform compatibility (Ubuntu/Debian/CentOS/RHEL/Fedora)
  * Fixed critical ASN data processing script issues
  * Enhanced error handling and user experience
  * Performance optimizations and monitoring
  * Complete documentation overhaul

 -- xt_asn Maintainer <maintainer@example.com>  Mon, 09 Sep 2025 19:30:00 +0000

xtables-addons-asn (2.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Added 4-byte ASN support (improved from original 2-byte ASN support)
  * Fixed compatibility issue with iptables-services (save and load rules)
  * Reworked ASN data update mechanism with centralized processing
  * Added comprehensive testing framework
  * Modernized build system with CMake support
  * Added systemd integration for automatic updates
  * Improved documentation and installation guides
  * Added DKMS support for automatic kernel module rebuilds
  * Enhanced error handling and logging
  * Performance optimizations for binary search algorithm
  * Added IPv6 support improvements
  * Fixed minor typos in iptables help messages

 -- xt_asn Maintainer <maintainer@example.com>  Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:00:00 +0000

